
 
                     CHEATING WITH THE ACTION REPLAY
                     ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~ 
                      ON AD&D AND ROLL PLAYING GAMES
                      ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
                          BY IAN ELDRIDGE © 1992
                          ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

                                  PART 3 
                                  ~~~~~~

       LEGEND OF FAERGHAIL
       ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
       Again to search for your Chars name use the FS command,in doing so
       you will find that 2 ADDRESSES will be found,both will look the
       same when you go into them so you will have to find out which one
       is the hackable one.I found that the second address was hackable
       and may be true in all cases but don't take my word for it.
       
       
       NOTE.
       ~~~~~
       When you edit your CHAR have the name to the far left(hex & ascii
       side) to make editing a lot easier.

LINE 1   41 53 4B 41 52 00 74 65 72 00 00 00 00 00 01 FF ASKAR.TER.......
LINE 2   FF 00 00 00 00 00 01 01 00 02 07 64 0A 0A 00 00 ...........D....
