       LINE 1
       ~~~~~~
       The chars name.

       LINE 2.
       ~~~~~~~
       This line holds % byte,DEATH byte and 1st byte of hit points.
LINE 2   FF 00 00 00 00 00 01 01 00 02 07 64 0A 0A 00 00 ...........D....
                                              ^  ^  ^  \->hit point
                                              |  |  | 
                                              |  |  ---DEATH byte
                                              |  |
                                              % bytes

     When your in the game the % byte is under the CHARS name at the top
     display.
     When you die 07 will be displayed in the position above,to bring your
     CHAR back to life just reset the hit point counter and delete the 07
     (00 the byte) and your CHAR will be revived.You will find that you
     will have to have an encounter in order to get rid of the bones and
     have your CHAR restored.This is true when altering most things.

        LINE 3.
        ~~~~~~~
        Line 3 holds hit points,negotiating ability,attack ability,defence
        ability,concentrating ability,pick pocketing & stalking.

LINE 3   06 00 06 02 11 00 11 11 00 00 31 00 00 00 00 00 ..........1.....        
          ^  ^  ^     ^     ^  ^        ^     ^        ^
          |  |  |     |     |  |        |     |        |
         hit points   na    aa da       ca    pp       s

         na = negotiating ability
         aa = attack ability
         da = defence ability
         ca = concentrating ability
         pp = pick pocketing
          s = stalking

        HIT POINTS.
        ~~~~~~~~~~~
        Change all 4 bytes,the 1st byte being the last byte on LINE 2,
        remembering the 1st 2 are a mirror of the last 2.
              EG.
                 00 06 00 06  change to 23 04 23 04
        One counts down the other is the MAX your CHAR can be restored to.
        23 04 is around 9000 hit points or so.

        ABILITYS.
        ~~~~~~~~~
        These can be changed to 64 being 100%.

        LINE 4.
        ~~~~~~~
        Line 4 holds trap detecting,trap disarming,lock picking.

LINE 4   00 05 00 05 00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 ................
             ^     ^     ^
             |     |     |
             |     |     lock picking 
             |     |
             |     trap disarming        change all to 64 (100%)
             |
             trap detecting

         LINE 5.
         ~~~~~~~
         This line holds your statts.

LINE 5   00 00 00 00 12 0E 0D 12 09 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 ................
                      ^  ^  ^  ^  ^
                      |  |  |  |  |
                      c  s  d  i  w

         c = constitution
         s = strength
         d = dexterity
         i = intelligence
         w = wizdom

         LINE 6.
         ~~~~~~~
         Line 6 holds magic points,no. of spells,no. of pack items,
         experiance & rations.

LINE 6   00 00 00 13 24 07 71 03 03 08 17 00 00 00 00 03 ....$.Q.........
                               ^  ^  ^  ^  ^  ^  ^  ^  ^
                               |  |  |  |  |  |  |  |  |
                               |  |  s  i  \  |  |  /  rations
                           spell points     \ |  | /
                                             \|  |/
                                           experience
          s = no. of spells in spell list.
          i = no. of items in your backpack.

         SPELL POINTS.
         ~~~~~~~~~~~~~
         The max for spell points is FF (255)
         
         If you change the items number you can have more items in your pack
         than you should.

         EXPERIENCE POINTS.
         ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
         The experience starts from the right and moves to the left,putting
         the value 7F FF FF FF will give your char over 32 billion points,
         put no more than 7F as last byte or you go into minus values.


         LINE 7.
         ~~~~~~~
         Line 7 holds money and 6 of the 7 languages.

LINE 7   00 00 00 00 FF 00 00 00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00 00 ................
                ^  ^  ^                 ^  ^  ^  ^  ^  ^
                |  |  |                 |  |  |  |  |  |
                 money                  an or li dw el da
         
         an = Animal
         or = Orc
         li = Lizard
         dw = Dwarven
         el = Elven
         da = Dark


         The money value starts from the right and moves to the left,putting
         FF in all 3 bytes gives you over 16 million creds,put the money
         straight in the bank cos your weight will be massively over loaded.

         To acquire all the languages just place a 01 in the byte,the last
         language is on LINE 8.
               E.G  01 01 01 01 01 01 <-gives 1st 6 languages


         LINE 8.
         ~~~~~~~
         Line 8 holds last of the languages and start of backpack items.

LINE 8   00 1A 00 00 64 28 00 00 64 09 00 00 64 08 00 00 ....D(..D...D...
          ^  \       /   \       /   \       /   \
          |   \     /     \     /     \     /     \
          m    \   /       \   /       \   /       \ 
                \ /         \ /         \ /         \
               item 1      item 2      item 3
         
         m = magic language 

         BACKPACK
         ~~~~~~~~
         The 1st byte in a item (E.G item 1) is the item number,for a full 
         list of items see the item list below.The last byte (64) is the
         % rating for the item,64 = 100% good,if the item gets damaged then
         the % goes down.

         WARNING.
         ~~~~~~~~
         If you place anything in your backpack just remember to readjust the
         no. of items in the backpack byte on LINE 6 above.


         LINE 9.
         ~~~~~~~
         Line 9 holds the start of the spell list.

LINE 9   00 01 08 02 04 03 09 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00 ................
             \ /   \ /   \ /
             (1)   (2)   (3)

         The 1st byte is the spell no. I.E spell 1 (1),spell 2 (2) ETC.
         
         The 2nd byte is the spell counter or how many of that spell you
         can cast,this byte you can change to FF (255) so you can cast the
         spell 255 times before running out.This is short term because 
         when you rest or save the game it will reset,it does come in handy
         when you are in combat though.

         LINE 10.
         ~~~~~~~~
         The start to the next CHAR.
         
